          "input_ue_unconnectable": {}
        }
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "# MODELS AND NODES USED IN THIS WORKFLOW\n\n---\n\n### Put all models in the models folder, organised into their respective subfolders.\n### If a required folder doesn't exist, create it.\n\n---\n\n## 🟣 LTX 2.3 Diffusion Model\nDownload **ltx-2.3-22b-distilled_transformer_only_fp8_input_scaled.safetensors** from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Lightricks/LTX-Video/resolve/main/ltx-2.3-22b-distilled_transformer_only_fp8_input_scaled.safetensors)\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models`\n\n---\n\n## 🟣 Audio VAE\nDownload **ltx-2.3-22b-distilled_audio_vae.safetensors** from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Lightricks/LTX-Video/resolve/main/ltx-2.3-22b-distilled_audio_vae.safetensors)\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/vae`\n\n---\n\n## 🟣 Video VAE\nDownload **ltx-2.3-22b-distilled_video_vae.safetensors** from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Lightricks/LTX-Video/resolve/main/ltx-2.3-22b-distilled_video_vae.safetensors)\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/vae`\n\n---\n\n## 🟣 Text Encoder (CLIP)\nDownload **gemma_3_12B_it_fp4_mixed.safetensors** from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/ltx-2/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/gemma_3_12B_it_fp4_mixed.safetensors)\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/text_encoders`\n\n---\n\n## 🟣 Spatial Upscaler\nDownload **ltx-2.3-spatial-upscaler-x2-1.1.safetensors** from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Lightricks/LTX-Video/resolve/main/ltx-2.3-spatial-upscaler-x2-1.1.safetensors)\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/latent_upscale_models`\n\n---\n\n## 🧩 Nodes Installed from ComfyUI Manager\n\n- **WhatDreamsCost-ComfyUI** — required for guide processing\n- **ComfyUI-VideoHelperSuite** — video preview and saving\n\nSearch for each by name in Manager → Custom Nodes → search\n\n---\n\n## 🟣 Muse Collective LTX Timeline Node\n\nInstall via Manager → **Install via Git URL:**\n"
      ],
      "color": "#EB6E33FF",
      "bgcolor": "#000"
    },
